summary: An ordinance relating to certain eminent domain proceedings for the condemnation of certain lands and other property for public street, highway, sewer, and drainage purposes across portions of Sections 3 and 4, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M., from Empire Way to East Marginal Way, pursuant to Ordinance No. 64895; providing for the discontinuance of such proceedings and repealing said Ordinance No. 64895.
